title: LSU kicker Trent Domingue -- unsure, shaky and blacked out -- came up with one ... - NOLA.com
text: Change Region comments LSU kicker Trent Domingue -- unsure, shaky and blacked out -- came up with one of the big moments of 2015 Trent Domingue, Vernon Hargreaves III LSU place kicker Trent Domingue (14) carries for a touchdown in front of Florida defensive back Vernon Hargreaves III (1) on a fake field goal in the second half of an NCAA college football game in Baton Rouge, La., Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015. LSU won 35-28. (AP Photo/Gerald Herbert) (Gerald Herbert | Associated Press)
